      <title>linux之vim文本编辑器</title>
      <link href="2021/09/14/vim/"/>
      <url>2021/09/14/vim/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="文本编辑工具vi-amp-vim"><a href="#文本编辑工具vi-amp-vim" class="headerlink" title="文本编辑工具vi&amp;vim"></a>文本编辑工具vi&amp;vim</h2><p><strong>vi的三种模式：</strong>command/edit/command-line 其主要功能和切换方式如下图所示。</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Hzx1998/imgpool/%E9%B8%9F%E5%93%A5%20Linux%20%E7%A7%81%E6%88%BF%E8%8F%9C%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%89%88.jpg"></p><p><strong>三种模式的基本指令介绍：</strong></p><p>当我们首次打开vi的时候首先进入的界面就是一般指令模式在这个模式下我们可以做图中所示的一些编辑操作：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;游标移动操作&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">j/ctrl+n #代表向下移动一行</span><br><span class="line">k/ctrl+p #代表向上移动一行</span><br><span class="line">h/backspace #代表向左移动一个字符</span><br><span class="line">l/space #代表向右移动一个字符</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">在前面加数字代表移动的距离</span></span><br><span class="line">n+space</span><br><span class="line">ctrl+f/b/d/u  #向下/向上移动一页  向下/向上移动半页</span><br><span class="line">+/- #光标移动到非空白字符下一行/上一行</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">0/$</span><span class="bash"> <span class="comment">#移动到当前行的第一个字符/最后一个字符</span></span></span><br><span class="line">G   #移动到最后一行</span><br><span class="line">nG   #移动到第n行</span><br><span class="line">gg   #移动到文件的第一列</span><br><span class="line">n+enter #光标向下移动n列</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;删除、复制、粘贴操作&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">###删除</span></span></span><br><span class="line">x,X #小写向后删除一个字符大写向前删除一个字符</span><br><span class="line">nx #向后删除n个字符</span><br><span class="line">dd #删除光标所在的一行</span><br><span class="line">ndd #删除光标所在下的n行</span><br><span class="line">d1G #删除光标所在行到第一行的所有数据</span><br><span class="line">dG #删除光标所在行到最后一行的所有数据</span><br><span class="line">d0 #删除光标到本行第一个字符的所有数据</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">d$</span><span class="bash"> <span class="comment">#删除光标到本行最后一个字符的所有数据</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">###复制</span></span></span><br><span class="line">yy #基本指令是yy  与上述dd相似有nyy  y1G yG y0 y$等操作</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">###粘贴</span></span></span><br><span class="line">p,P #小写将已复制的数据在光标下一行粘贴  大写在光标上一行</span><br><span class="line">J  #将光标所在列与下一列数据结合成同一列</span><br><span class="line">c       #重复删除多个数据</span><br><span class="line">u       #复原前一个动作</span><br><span class="line">ctrl+r  #重做上一个动作</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>一般指令模式可以通过以下几种操作进入插入模式：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">i/I #小写表示从目前光标所在处插入大写表示目前所在行的第一个非空白字符插入</span><br><span class="line">a/A #小写表示目前光标所在的下一个字符处插入大写表示从本行最后一个字符处插入</span><br><span class="line">o/O #小写表示目前光标所在行的下一行插入新一行大写表示目前光标上一行插入新的一行</span><br><span class="line">r/R #进入取代模式 小写取代光标所在字符一次 大写一直取代光标所在字符</span><br><span class="line">Esc #退出</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>命令模式主要有以下一些操作：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;搜寻与取代&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">/word #光标之后查找一个单词</span><br><span class="line">?word #光标之前查找一个单词</span><br><span class="line">n/N #使用以上命令后继续操作</span><br><span class="line">:num1,num2s/word1/word2/g   #在num1和num2行之间查询word1并用word2取代:1,$s第一列到最后一列 /gc表示最后加confirm确认操作</span><br><span class="line">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;存储与退出&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">:w</span><br><span class="line">:w!</span><br><span class="line">:q</span><br><span class="line">:q!</span><br><span class="line">:wq</span><br><span class="line">:wq!</span><br><span class="line">ZZ   #文件没变动则不保存离开，有变动则保存离开</span><br><span class="line">:w filename  #另存为新文件</span><br><span class="line">:r filename  #在编辑的数据中读入另一个文件的数据</span><br><span class="line">:n1,n2 w filename</span><br><span class="line">:! command</span><br><span class="line">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;vim环境的变更&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">:set nu #显示行号</span><br><span class="line">:set nonu #取消显示行号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此为常用指令，但是vim指令不止这些，但是我们没必要也很难记住全部的指令，所以等到需要的时候查表即可</p>]]></content>
      
      
